snippet.title: "She Flirts Her Way" Emilia Clarke Reveals Why Amber Heard is not Fired Yet...
snippet.description:
"She Flirts Her Way" Emilia Clarke Reveals Why Amber Heard is not Fired Yet...
Fans of Johnny Depp have created a change.org petition to have Amber Heard removed from Mara, and the number of people signing it has risen in recent weeks. Unfortunately, many things have been rearranged as a result of the occurrences that occurred during 2020. What I mean is that a lot of comic book movies that were intended to be released were unable to do so, but on the plus side, things are looking brighter. This may not be the case in 2021, since comic book films, like other films, will likely resume their usual release dates.
